{"tid":1240593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(反洗腦)其實有一次性引渡條文引渡凶手去台灣","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:37:36.000Z","uid":190431,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3776fcdebee19fa54616df3f34a113bc4d00c6","tid":1240593,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"一早有大律師指出有一次性引渡條文，可以引渡凶手去台灣，唔需要修例，係林鄭借單野去推修例，扮無其他方法。<br />\n<br />\n自從暫停修例之後，facebook藍絲出現好多改圖話個凶手多謝黃絲們，又話黃絲唔理公義。<br />\n<br />\n今次林鄭好可能為左完謊，林鄭又咁要面，好可能會自我預言實踐，寧願放佢出黎都唔會用一次性引渡條文。<br />\n<br />\n同埋希望有改圖高手，整番幾張圖，解釋清楚，反洗腦。"},{"pid":"6d2b61a40ab2d0cfb070d4b8e192c0b349b94992","tid":1240593,"uid":190431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"希望有改圖高手，出手幫助，家陣藍絲係咁用呢樣野黎老屈，一定要解釋清楚。"},{"pid":"2f21e53ce89eabd4f9186c6ef98a990c357c4092","tid":1240593,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"54292d7a9cfd1ce73b3ae1d2a44f46db0331e34b","tid":1240593,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57d1d37033a30f95228abe059eaf26f43743ae13","tid":1240593,"uid":190431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe443a081e9877b4b57c9bad8f17733682349782","tid":1240593,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"542ad3e82194c8a4f5fa593deeb39332cbdce3a1","tid":1240593,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9117646322a6e393f6bb0f0beb322ff4932eb776","tid":1240593,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"